stories.text:
We're interested in sending swag to contributors for our open source kubernetes tools. We'd like to ship to all over the world, ideally include more then one item in a package, and not handle any of the shipping and packaging ourselves.

Does anyone have experience with any of the online platforms that do this? Would love to hear recommendations.

Our budget is $25-$50 per package including worldwide shipping.
